arStrings.szText:
Each {c_important}Trade Agreement{/c} with this Mercenary has an additional {c_number}+10%{/c} chance for the item to be offered when {c_important}Bartering{/c}.

{c_important}Trade Agreements{/c} can be unlocked in the Mercenary Den, adding additional item types to a Mercenary's {c_important}Bartering{/c} potential.
